author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Precise Biometrics says BioMatch integrated in two smartphones
text:
Sept 30 Precise Biometrics AB
* Precise Biometrics says Precise BioMatch Mobile integrated in two smartphones from leading American tech company through cooperation with Fingerprint Cards
* Says will receive license fees from Q3 2015 onwards Further company coverage: (Reporting by Stockholm Newsroom)
